{"tid":870202,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"資深甘草藝人岳華加國離世　終年76歲","createTime":"2018-10-21T02:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T08:02:22.000Z","uid":130105,"like":53,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"eebd9c4f310521445b6f71738a6cf9b9a117a7f8","tid":870202,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1RKM99hafh48h9bpbB3R4Bk6G-bl3Akcc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1RKM99hafh48h9bpbB3R4Bk6G-bl3Akcc&h=12156a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1BG7i6Adtdpa6gNyU4p6Hu0vuKiut0xUY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1BG7i6Adtdpa6gNyU4p6Hu0vuKiut0xUY&h=3cba094c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1b0Qs1mTbsrgo2uxawbl3eT_gSiNkMj9V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1b0Qs1mTbsrgo2uxawbl3eT_gSiNkMj9V&h=29c4fb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1gkS35dx5xy4RdongdaaAjMtOTlpwnGmN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1gkS35dx5xy4RdongdaaAjMtOTlpwnGmN&h=b9d9dd5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=17lB_-5dHxFro64cTpODS3LQI1C5ZSfbk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D17lB_-5dHxFro64cTpODS3LQI1C5ZSfbk&h=4b9efb07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=11xhNnbe5GEZoCamExYsd63ZfoDokcZMb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D11xhNnbe5GEZoCamExYsd63ZfoDokcZMb&h=9fcecb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nR.I.P.<br />\n<br />\n資深實力派甘草演員岳華傳出在加拿大時間昨天不幸離世的消息，終年76歲。據加拿大的電台人士指，當時岳華太太恬妮及女兒Faye均陪伴在側。而好友張之珏亦向東網證實岳華逝世。<br />\n<br />\n張之珏指消息是恬妮透過短訊告知張之珏妹妹張寶之，二人得知後亦非常傷心，張之珏亦已向岳華女兒表達悼念之情。張續指與岳華相識超過30年，對上一次見面已是半年前。他又大讚岳華為人低調，早年生病時唔想見人，但仍會相約他及其妹到酒店見面，每年又會邀約食大閘蟹等。<br />\n<br />\n而另一好友林建明亦指昨晚收到消息，她說：「尋晚十點到收到朋友消息，話岳華啱啱喺溫哥華去世，入咗醫院只係兩日，恬妮唔想人打擾佢，估計多數係癌症，因為朋友8月時見到佢瘦得好厲害。」 <br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAekbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=30c0e702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n岳華變甘草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eada827888a9ef6bf08a21ec5126774e940ac2","tid":870202,"uid":59283,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚愛國走去拎加拿大護照<br />\n四年前d反佔領言論一世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50eb0d66fd1b96d7a15f0d8fbee3d1b8a1214ff3","tid":870202,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:43:20.000Z","msg":"近排重播既情越海岸線仲有佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f2e3c6ef8dd422d5e11fc0b9c6261ebf10a6bc","tid":870202,"uid":42586,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"抵啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a639a53c58fb293368a34f269d5bafdfe80f584b","tid":870202,"uid":62815,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"講到咁愛港死都返加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9c726ecfa56fda3270be878dc7449ebeec38bf","tid":870202,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a639a53c58fb293368a34f269d5bafdfe80f584b","tid":870202,"uid":62815,"like":28,"dislike":1,"s